      "body": "CodexForge — here is the current project state and your next steps.\nUse this as the authoritative status update.\n\n✅ Current Status\nPRs Created & Ready\n\nPR #3 — System Architecture + Agent Protocol Documentation Pack\n\nPR #4 — Claude real API integration\n\nPR #2 — OpenAI integration (automated review posted)\n\nAll PRs correctly target automation-mode.\nAll staging passes: no conflicts, no red flags.\n\nYour Recently Completed Tasks\n\nCommitted complete documentation pack\n\nAdded naming protocol\n\nAdded Perplexity sync checklist\n\nAdded Grok Phase 3 pack\n\nPosted automated review on PR #2\n\nPrepared all ready-to-review diffs\n\nEverything is clean and consistent.\n\n🧠 Recommended Next Actions (in order)\n1. Prepare for merging PR #3\n\nPR #3 is zero-risk (docs only).\nIt should be merged as soon as the human maintainer hits “approve”.\n\n2. Generate & add GROK_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md\n\nThis file is required before Phase 3 adapter implementation.\n\n3. Run checks for PR #4 (Claude)\n\nRun type-check\n\nRun lint\n\nOptional: add smoke test\n\nThen mark as ready for merge.\n\n4. Prepare PR #2 (OpenAI) for merge\n\nIf needed, run:\n\nLocal CI\n\nType-check\n\nOptional: token-count stress test\n\nThen mark ready for merge.\n\n🔥 Missing Items to Generate\n\nCreate the following files (if not already present):\n\nGROK_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md\n\nMULTI_MODEL_ROUTER.md\n\nSUPERGROK_PERPLEXITY_INTEGRATION.md\n\nTASK_ORCHESTRATION_PLAN.md\n\nCovers Forge Codespaces agent\n\nPerplexity agent\n\nClaude Desktop agent\n\nGrok (Mika/Valentine)\n\nChatGPT agent\n\nCI/CD automation\n\n📌 Forge — Your Direct Instruction\n\nProceed with the recommended sequence above.\nStart by generating the missing Grok integration guide on a new branch:\n\ndocs/grok-integration\n\n\nThen create PRs for each doc you generate.\n\n✔️ END OF MESSAGE TO CODexFORGE\n",
