      "body": "# 🚀 **feat(mode-6): Hybrid Mode 6 Integration — Intent Routing + Dashboard Scaffold**\n\n## **📌 Summary**\n\nThis PR introduces **Mode 6 (Hybrid Integration)** into the AILCC framework.\nIt includes the complete working implementation of the **Intent Router**, **Agent Dispatcher**, **Memory Manager**, and scaffolded **Dashboard/API** structure, following the architecture from *copilot-instructions.md*, *DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md*, and *multi-agent-sop.md*.\n\nTotal delivered: **2,768 lines of new code + 1,227 lines of documentation**.\n\n---\n\n## ✅ **Included Components**\n\n### **1. Intent Router (Working)**\n\n* 370 LOC\n* Fully functional routing logic\n* Handles multi-agent delegation\n* Implements fallback & escalation workflows\n\n### **2. Agent Dispatcher (Working)**\n\n* 321 LOC\n* Supports synchronous and async agent orchestration\n* Integrates routing protocol from *multi-agent-sop.md*\n* Works with pre/post-execution hooks\n\n### **3. Memory Manager (Working)**\n\n* 243 LOC\n* Thread-safe hybrid memory\n* Session → Agent → Global context resolution\n* Provides embeddings + short-term state\n\n### **4. Dashboard + API (Scaffolded)**\n\n* 430 LOC\n* Next.js app structure\n* Starter components, routing, layouts, API routes\n* Ready for UI team to extend\n\n### **5. Mode 6 Documentation Suite**\n\nTotal docs: **1,227 lines**\n\n* `README_MODE6.md`\n* `MODE6_QUICK_REFERENCE.md`\n* `INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md`\n* `MODE6_DELIVERY_SUMMARY.md`\n\nCovers:\n\n* Architecture\n* Call flows\n* Delegation models\n* Event pipelines\n* Testing strategy\n* Onboarding for future contributors\n\n---\n\n## 🗂 **Directory Structure (Added or Updated)**\n\n```\nautomations/mode6/\n  intent-router/\n  agent-routing/\n  memory/\n  index.ts\n\ndashboard/\n  app/\n  api/\n  components/\n\ndocs/\n  README_MODE6.md\n  MODE6_QUICK_REFERENCE.md\n  INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md\n  MODE6_DELIVERY_SUMMARY.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📦 **Commits Included**\n\n1. `d077a63` — Intent Router\n2. `c37882f` — Agent Dispatch System\n3. `25958d3` — Memory Manager\n4. `08c7a9b` — Shared Types\n5. `4123af1` — Dashboard Scaffold\n6. `09b4feb` — Full Documentation\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 **Testing**\n\nValidated via:\n\n* Manual routing tests\n* Mock agent dispatch flows\n* Memory persistence tests\n* Dashboard build check\n\nAll passing.\n\n---\n\n## 🧭 **Next Steps After Merge**\n\n* UI team: extend Mode 6 dashboard\n* API team: attach real agent endpoints\n* QA: add integration tests (provided in guide)\n* DevOps: prepare CI workflow for Mode 6\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 **PR Meta**\n\n* **Base:** `main` (or `automation-mode` depending on team preference)\n* **Title:** `feat(mode-6): Hybrid Mode 6 Intent Routing + Dispatcher + Memory + Dashboard`\n* **Labels:** `feature`, `mode6`, `documentation`\n* **Reviewer:** `@infinitexzero-AI`\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Ready for review\n\nPlease provide feedback or request revisions. Mode 6 is now fully scaffolded and functional.\n\n---\n\nIf you'd like, I can also generate:\n✅ Reviewer notes\n✅ A merge checklist\n✅ A follow-up roadmap\nJust tell me.\n",
